<content>
    <para id="id1172467506211">Please take a few minutes to reflect on the collaboration of each of your group members during the project. You will need to assign a percentage for each group member based on the following attributes:</para>
    <list id="id1172474912431" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Work Ethic</item>
      <item>Time Management</item>
      <item>On-task Behavior</item>
      <item>Cooperation</item>
      <item>Contribution</item>
      <item>Initiative</item>
      <item>Follow-through</item>
      <item>Attendance</item>
    </list>
    <para id="id1172469529321">Please do not give any group member a perfect score of 100%, and be sure to offer a detailed rationale for the percentage that you give. <emphasis effect="bold">If you assign a group member 100%, or if you do not offer an adequate rationale, you will need to re-do your evaluations.</emphasis></para>
